casebody.data:
No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 1065.]

Second motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is allowed a total of $30,391.20 for the period September 1, 1989, through January 23, 1991, to be paid equally by the parties. Request of the Special Master to be discharged granted, and Monte Pasco is hereby discharged with the thanks of the Court.
